abstract: The UnitedHealth Group posted lower-than-expected first-quarter earnings and sharply reduced its outlook for 2008, saying fewer businesses and employees were signing up.
snippet: The UnitedHealth Group posted lower-than-expected first-quarter earnings and sharply reduced its outlook for 2008, saying fewer businesses and employees were signing up.
lead_paragraph: It is never a good thing if many of your customers can no longer afford what you are selling.

headline.main: Insurer Says Economy Has Dented Its Prospects
